Hello,

Here is the output of 'ddccontrol -p -c -d' for my monitor Samsung 
SyncMaster P2350. It identifies itself with a Plug and Play ID SAM0525. 
The parameters for the MagicBright setting are stored at 0xdc. I have 
figured out the following values:
1 -> Text
2 -> Internet
3 -> Game
4 -> Sport
5 -> Movie
6 -> Custom

Regards,
Raj Kiran

